Version 1.0-pre0	16/07/2006
- Initial release
Version 1.1 		21/07/2006
- Add WBMP support for partial compatibility with libGD.
- add Perl bindings for client library available in lang-bindings
  subdirectory.
- add example perl scripts in contrib directory.
- add rpm.spec file to archive
- misc bugfixes
